snippet.title: Goldie Escapes Megan in Roblox - M3GAN Story
snippet.description:
Goldie roleplays in roblox. She gets adopted my Gemma and Caddy. Things seems to be so fun at first but than Megan becomes overprotective of Caddy. Will she want to get rid of Goldie now that shes part of the family? Find out what happens in this Roblox Spooky Story.
